author: @useryoutubehandle
text:
Idk but out of all of their dances, this choreo is a 'meh' for me. It has subtle movements which doesn't need a strong energy and it's fine, but it has LOTS of walking. They walk to their positions showing their backs a lot of times. Mina's part at 0:40, why does she have to go to a far position? I'm literally looking at her cause she's at the center, then my eyes still followed her and I didn't even notice Jeongyeon going to the center. In BB performance, there's literally a split second where no one is at the center because Mina rushed to her next position, and Jeongyeon is still catching up. (Edit: Watching Mina's part in the moving ver. which has close up is huhuhu coz she's still singing. It reminds me of her first part in Scientist, she moves to her next position, turning her back while singing 'anido') 

Also, I don't even know what's happening at 0:50 and 1:52 but it looks messy. ğŸ˜­ Don't get me wrong, I know all their dances that's why I can't help but feel disappointed with this. Momo and Mina's second part is a banger tho. This is my opinion, pls don't hate me.
